description: Updates the user hierarchy structure: add, remove, and rename user hierarchy levels.

parameters.name: HierarchyStructure
parameters.description: The hierarchy levels to update. LevelOne (dict) --- The update for level one. The name of the user hierarchy level. Must not be more than 50 characters. LevelTwo (dict) --- The update for level two. LevelThree (dict) --- The update for level three. LevelFour (dict) --- The update for level four. LevelFive (dict) --- The update for level five. Must not be more than 50 characters.
